risk: medium
confidence: 75
resolution: Registered list options accumulate through Commander and preserve values through loose-option reconciliation.
expected_result: "One, comma-separated, repeated, and aliased list values reach extension handlers in occurrence order."
actual_result: The loose parser replaced Commander-parsed list values with an empty array when no loose occurrences remained.
regression: true
